{"tid":1783103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［是晚任務］帶領劇集收視創本年新低嘅黎耀祥代言嘅正官庒","createTime":"2019-12-14T13:47:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T16:46:20.000Z","uid":75759,"like":62,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"b73893238d39d5f180d57bef7cea054e14cff4a0","tid":1783103,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T13:47:19.000Z","msg":"是晚精選@14/12<br />\n正官庄<br />\n<a href=\"https://facebook.com/ckjhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Fckjhk&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWiL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=a2fbe7db\" target=\"_blank\">https://facebook.com/ckjhk</a><br />\n👆去派嬲兼留言👆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RppvNcg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRppvNcg.jpg&h=2441fdf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正官庄素來與CCTVB關係密切，產品放上Big Big Shop賣不特止，仲搵話批評TVB嘅人係冇良心嘅黎耀祥代言！😡<br />\n士多網站都有佢哋啲嘢賣，擺明間公司係深藍啦！🔵<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">聽聞佢哋想吸引年青顧客</span></strong>，咁就更加應該終止一切與TVB嘅合作喇！<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n黎耀祥：好多人覺得踩低TVB就係知識份子<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/35lNxx1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F35lNxx1&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWiL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=4e374c4f\" target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/35lNxx1</a><br />\n<br />\n【抵制CCTVB 任務流程】<br />\n基本：<br />\n1.派嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.洗版 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.罷買<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.互Like留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n進階：<br />\n5.放張抵制圖留言以示不滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n6.負評 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請用幾秒去派嬲、留言、推post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俾幾秒我哋抵制TVB團隊得唔得? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n留言template，爭取客戶唔簽2020年廣告合約，歡迎創意留言：<br />\n無綫新聞，歪曲事實，出賣港人！本人明白貴公司或已簽訂今年合約，未能即時撤回廣告，故暫時罷用。請貴公司承諾不簽訂2020 TVB廣告合約，不以無綫藝人代言，產品從無綫網購平台上下架，及撤回與其所有的商業合作，否則將列入「永久抵制名單」，永不錄用。<br />\n記得放埋圖片：<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/1u619D6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1u619D6.png&h=71d344ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://na.cx/i/1u619D6.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1u619D6.png&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWiL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=c11d1f85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://na.cx/i/1u619D6.png</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記得bookmark: TVB廣告客戶名單！！ <br />\n消費前諗清楚 <br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2P7cPeD&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWiL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=e3b0d3e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD</a> <br />\n－－－－－－－ <br />\n請即follow: <br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWiL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=da0a605d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb</a><br />\nIG: #sayno2tvb<br />\nTG 綜合狙擊頻道: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWiL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=d411506f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2tvb</a><br />\nTG 後備狙擊頻道: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2tvb2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb2&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWiL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=be43d464\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2tvb2</a><br />\nTG CCTVB記者實時位置狙擊頻道: <a href=\"https://t.me/nomoretvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fnomoretvb&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWiL1b